{"tid":1427450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人]發夢個陣收過尿袋既男仔","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:24:47.000Z","uid":88141,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"999f431f62a5c5fa3b34b13ae43cd4a0fd7f29eb","tid":1427450,"uid":88141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:12:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻大家<br />\n<br />\n話說我同朋友7月頭發夢 食完野坐左係到<br />\n<br />\n突然有個男仔同我地講野 然後俾我地捉住同佢傾計<br />\n<br />\n最後佢先唔好意思話其實電話冇電 想借尿袋用<br />\n<br />\n我即刻送左個尿袋俾佢<br />\n<br />\n好想知佢最近過得好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來都唔想搵 大家各自安好就得 但係發生左咁多事<br />\n<br />\n好擔心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果各位巴絲 知道有個男仔7月頭曾經發過夢<br />\n又有人送過尿袋俾佢 可唔可以叫佢聯絡我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb3628853a953b592a61b44ecc0bdd4e4f7e781","tid":1427450,"uid":88141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"64807365f2c9491c8f686b766582f8ff9d5eeb84","tid":1427450,"uid":88141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1540d5125fc7c0a8caeac4801f17ce2c247cb0da","tid":1427450,"uid":88141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:15:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55a49086379a8038d9246650d9ae777c9d5c9f9f","tid":1427450,"uid":91314,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"你想拎返尿袋定想成個人拎走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji